# Guluä
Guluä will be a cream-colored [[Races/Dragon\|dragon]], bonded to [[Characters/Cole\|Cole]]. Notably, Guluä was the last egg that [[Dragons/Kveykva\|Kveykva]] had before her body-death; her egg was kept safe by [[Characters/Malkyn Warhound\|Malkyn Warhound]] and [[Characters/Talia Stormchaser\|Talia Stormchaser]] for years, finally hatching for Cole in a rather fitting surprise.

Born to [[Dragons/Kveykva\|Kveykva]] and [[Dragons/Vahren\|Vahren]].
